  <div id="text-content_861069C0-1D49-0135-1ECC-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can change the default language for your entire account. Canvas supports a variety of languages. This change will override any browser/OS language settings.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Users can select a preferred language in their user settings, which will override the account default.</p>
  </div>
